span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109551\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109551)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109551)\">1 Cor. 13:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116229\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116229)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116229)\">D&amp;C 129:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111382\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111382)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111382)\">Jacob 2:40<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116413\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116413)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116413)\">D&amp;C 132:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106936\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106936)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106936)\">Prov. 13:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113975\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113975)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113975)\">D&amp;C 50:29-30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114860\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114860)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114860)\">D&amp;C 88:64-65<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106325\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106325)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106325)\">Deut. 28:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107212\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107212)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107212)\">Isa. 50:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116505\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116505)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116505)\">D&amp;C 133:70<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111107\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111107)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111107)\">2 Ne. 2:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111983\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111983)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111983)\">Alma 17:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115386\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115386)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115386)\">D&amp;C 106:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116777\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116777)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116777)\">Moses 5:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106899\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106899)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106899)\">Ps. 144:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110944\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110944)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110944)\">1 Ne. 8:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111097\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111097)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111097)\">2 Ne. 2:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111153\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111153)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111153)\">2 Ne. 5:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"c